text: Tiana the baddest princess out here. The movie was made November 25, 2009. Tiana is a hard-working person who wanted nothing but to open up her own finest restaurant in New Orleans in memory of her father. The grown voice behind tiana was Anika Noni Rose & the child her was Elizabeth M. Dampier. One night of tiana’s best friend’s birthday party she made a promise to a frog to help him become a prince again and return for him to help her open up her the biggest restaurant in New Orleans. later down the road twisted things start to come up and you’ll just have to watch the movie to find out. == References == Category:Disney characters
title: Tiana (The Princess and the Frog)
